                    de.unirostock.sems.cbarchive.CombineArchiveException,
                    java.net.URISyntaxException,
                    javax.xml.transform.TransformerException
        Reads in the given COBRAme JSON file and converts it to the CombineArchive of the SBMLme representation with the respective SBML and SBOL files.
        Parameters:
        jsonFile - the JSON file of the COBRAme model
        output - the prefix of the output files
        modelName - the name of the model in SBML
        validation - whether the created SBML model should be validated, currently does not involve the validity of the SBMLme attributes.
        tidy - whether the documents should be printed tidy.
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException
        org.sbolstandard.core2.SBOLValidationException
        org.sbml.jsbml.text.parser.ParseException
        org.sbml.jsbml.SBMLException
        javax.xml.stream.XMLStreamException
        org.sbolstandard.core2.SBOLConversionException
        org.jdom2.JDOMException
        java.text.ParseException
        de.unirostock.sems.cbarchive.CombineArchiveException
        java.net.URISyntaxException
        javax.xml.transform.TransformerException

      • addMEProcessDataFromJSON

        public void addMEProcessDataFromJSON(org.sbml.jsbml.Model model,
                                     java.util.List<com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonNode> processDataSBML)
        Adds ProcessData information from the list of reaction independent process data of the JSON file. To be more specific the list of process data includes all StoichiometricData, SubreactionData and TranslocationData objects.
        Parameters:
        model - the SBML model
        processDataSBML - the list of process data objects that do not encode information of a single reaction

      • addReactionsFromJSON

        public void addReactionsFromJSON(org.sbml.jsbml.Model model,
                                 org.sbolstandard.core2.SBOLDocument sbol,
                                 org.sbml.jsbml.ext.groups.GroupsModelPlugin groups,
                                 org.sbml.jsbml.ext.fbc.Objective objective,
                                 java.util.List<com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonNode> reactions,
                                 java.util.LinkedHashMap<java.lang.String,com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonNode> processData)
                          throws org.sbml.jsbml.text.parser.ParseException,
                                 org.sbolstandard.core2.SBOLValidationException
        Adds all reactions from a list of JsonNodes to the SBML and SBOL models according to their type. Also adds all process data information to the reaction annotations that is not added to the model annotation by the addMEProcessDataFromJSON(Model, List) method.
        Parameters:
        model - the SBML model
        sbol - the SBOL document
        groups - the GroupsModelPlugin of the SBML model
        objective - the objective of the model
        reactions - the list of reactions from the JSON file
        processData - the map of process data objects that encode additional reaction specific information
        Throws:
        org.sbml.jsbml.text.parser.ParseException
        org.sbolstandard.core2.SBOLValidationException
